    div
    .panel-body
      h2(class="project-title") HTML
      p HyperText Markup Language
      br
      p When it comes to creating a web page, there are three parts:
      p(class="indent") 1. The content to be displayed. The WHAT - HTML
      p(class="indent") 2. What the content will look like - CSS
      p(class="indent") 3. How to make the content DO something - JavaScript
      br
      p An HTML document is made up of a head and a body.
      p Everything in HTML is defined within tags
      br
      img(src="/images/htmlHead.png")

