      p Cascading Style Sheets
      br
      p CSS consists of selectors, and declarations
      p A declaration is a property name followed by a property value
      br
      p
        img(src="/images/css.png")
      br
      p Here's a 
        a(href="http://www.w3schools.com/cssref/" target="_blank") list
        |  of CSS property names and possible values to choose from

